sourcesContent:
import Pikachu from './images/pikachu.png'
import Bulbasaur from './images/bulbasaur.png'
import Charmander from './images/charmander.png'
import Koffing from './images/koffing.png'
import Magikarp from './images/magikarp.png'
import Meowth from './images/meowth.png'
import Mewtwo from './images/mewtwo.png'
import Psyduck from './images/psyduck.png'
import Snorlax from './images/snorlax.png'
import Squirtle from './images/squirtle.png'



export const pokemons = [
    { name: 'Pikachu', description: 'Pikachu that can generate powerful electricity have cheek sacs that are extra soft and super stretchy.', type: ['electric'], category: 'mouse', img: Pikachu },
    { name: 'Bulbasaur', description: 'There is a plant seed on its back right from the day this Pokémon is born. The seed slowly grows larger.', type: ['grass', 'poison'], category: 'seed', img: Bulbasaur },
    { name: 'Squirtle', description: 'When it retracts its long neck into its shell, it squirts out water with vigorous force.', type: ['water'], category: 'tiny turtle', img: Squirtle },
    { name: 'Charmander', description: 'It has a preference for hot things. When it rains, steam is said to spout from the tip of its tail.', type: ['fire'], category: 'lizard', img: Charmander },
    { name: 'Meowth', description: 'It loves to collect shiny things. If it’s in a good mood, it might even let its Trainer have a look at its hoard of treasures.', type: ['normal'], category: 'scratch cat', img: Meowth },
    { name: 'Psyduck', description: 'Psyduck is constantly beset by headaches. If the Pokémon lets its strange power erupt, apparently the pain subsides for a while.', type: ['water'], category: 'duck', img: Psyduck },
    { name: 'Koffing', description: 'Its body is full of poisonous gas. It floats into garbage dumps, seeking out the fumes of raw, rotting trash.', type: ['poison'], category: 'poison gas', img: Koffing },
    { name: 'Magikarp', description: 'It is virtually worthless in terms of both power and speed. It is the most weak and pathetic Pokémon in the world.', type: ['water'], category: 'fish', img: Magikarp },
    { name: 'Snorlax', description: 'It is not satisfied unless it eats over 880 pounds of food every day. When it is done eating, it goes promptly to sleep.', type: ['normal'], category: 'sleeping', img: Snorlax },
    { name: 'Mewtwo', description: 'Its DNA is almost the same as Mew’s. However, its size and disposition are vastly different.', type: ['psychic'], category: 'genetic', img: Mewtwo },
]
